Pillai 

Pillai <- function(E,B,g){
  inv.E <- solve(E)  #  
  lambda <- eigen(inv.E %*% B)$values  # E^-1B 
  s <- min(length(lambda),g-1)  # min(p, g-1)
  V <- 0  # Pillai  initialize
  for(i in 1:s){
    V <- V + lambda[i]/(1+lambda[i])
  }
  
  return(V)
}

Lawley-Hotelling 

Lawley_Hotelling <- function(E,B,g){
  inv.E <- solve(E)  #  
  lambda <- eigen(inv.E %*% B)$values  # E^-1B 
  s <- min(length(lambda),g-1)  # min(p, g-1)
  U <- sum(lambda)  # Lawley-Hotelling 
  
  return(U)
}

Roy 

Roy <- function(E,B){
  inv.E <- solve(E)  #  
  lambda.1 <- eigen(inv.E %*% B)$values[1]  # E^-1B   (lambda_1)
  theta <- lambda.1/(1+lambda.1)  # Roy 
  
  return(theta)
}
Roy(E,B)
